metadata.description: GodMode is a collection of 1,000 community-generated NFTs rooted in utility. Each GodMode NFT unlocks unlimited claim access to analytical bounties at Flipside Crypto. Additionally, the NFT grants exclusive access to the gated GodMode section of Flipside’s Discord. Once inside, you’ll have access to the most gifted minds in crypto analytics, analytics training sessions for project analytics, early access to Flipside product launches, and much more.
